April is #CommunityCollegeAwarenessMonth!🏫
Comm. colleges are as vital to our communities as Higher Ed is to our nation’s future. They offer:
👥Smaller classes;
⏰ Flexible schedules;
📚 Different courses;
📚 Transferable credits; 
💵Affordable tuition; &amp;
📜Accessible education. https://t.co/vHUtBWuVJI
